Many colleagues and fans have showered praises on Destiny Etiko for offering scholarship to her gateman’s daughter. The actress on Wednesday announced that her gateman’s daughter has been offered scholarship to university level by her foundation. Etiko acknowledged her love for the lady and coveted God’s help to fulfill the pledge. The actress shared photos of her gateman’s daughter and wrote: And the beautiful melanin daughter of my gateman just (got) a scholarship from DESTINY ETIKO FOUNDATION to further her Education to university level. LOVER HER SO MUCH @destinyetikofoundation_. So help us Lord.” Reacting to the humanitarian gesture by Etiko towards her gateman’s daughter, colleagues and fans hailed and prayed for her. Ejine Okoroafor said: “God bless you.” Chika Lann wrote: “Oh, I love this… May God continue to bless your beautiful heart.”   I didn’t convert to Islam, says Jim Iyke     Four Nigerian celebrities who underwent liposuction     Condemning ladies with plastic butt unacceptable- Nazo…   Dave Ogbeni stated: “God bless you. Bless you real good.” Uchenna Nnanna said: “Nne God bless you.” Jane Obi wrote: “blessed dramadoll.” browny_brave stated: “Big Etiko God bless you.” chidoxflash said: “May God continue to bless your good heart. You are a blessing to our generation.” emmy_bwoy12 wrote: “It’s not about being rich and famous, it’s about your assistance and love to others who needs it as well, God continue to bless u destiny.” abikegrocerystore stated: “God bless you and all that concerns you momma.” lizzynwankwo said: “Wow! That’s so kind of you, congratulations to the pretty girl. God’s blessings always.”